<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link280268" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=280268&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F574932-to-sew-clothes-the-indian-woman-and-matt%2Fanswers%2F280268-usually-bits-of-bone">flag</a>
