    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3576315252" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17453391661666279651">Another reviewer said this is a five star book for late elementary/early middle, and it is! Elizabeth George Spear tells great stories that bring historical periods to life. My 5th grader’s imagination was immediate sparked by the possibilities of living alone in the woods, preparing a home for her family. I loved The Bronze Bow when I was a middle schooler and I’m finally catching up and reading the rest of her books! </span>

          </span>
        </div>


